data.description: This recently updated 4 bed 2 bath home is turn key and waiting for you. There's plenty of room for entertaining with its large open living room as you enter that wraps around to an even larger dining room. The kitchen is equipped with newer appliances and granite counter tops and the main level boast durable LVP flooring throughout. Upstairs you'll find 4 generously size bedrooms, a full bath and a loft area perfect for a home office or kid play zone. You'll enjoy the plush soft carpeting throughout the second floor keeping your feet warm and the sun on your face through the big bay windows in the loft. The basement is partially finished with new fresh drywall, just waiting on your final touches to make it your own. Your new home is conveniently located to everywhere you'd want to be! Across the street from Hackberry Park, a short drive to Lincoln, Fremont and Omaha and just moments away from Beautiful Lake Wanahoo.
